s: Summary: Private afternoon mixer “Trade the World” hosted by Aster, Opinion and WLFI with a live trading challenge.
Topics: Market making, DEX liquidity, competitive trading strategies, cross‑chain arbitrage.
Speakers: Representatives from Aster, Opinion, World Liberty Financial and media partner Hanora.
r: Test and showcase your trading instincts in a real‑time challenge.
Network with active market makers and liquidity providers.
Expose your project to potential institutional and retail capital.
